public abstract class AbstractQuantileEstimation<SAMPLE extends AbstractQuantileEstimation.AbstractSample<SAMPLE>> extends Object
A memory efficient abstract implementation for calculating quantile summaries.
See Also:
  • "Greenwald and Khanna, 'Space-efficient online computation of quantile summaries' SIGMOD 2001"
